thread.title: New York City Olive Oil Competition Heats Up

author: Charles Passy
title: New York City Olive Oil Competition Heats Up

organizations.name: new york international olive oil competition

text:
At the New York International Olive Oil Competition, the most prized commodity may be a plate of apple slices.
As 18 judges sample their way through nearly 1,000 different oils from 27 countries for this annual event, they frequently need to refresh their palates. Apple slices and the occasional spoonful of plain yogurt typically do the trick.
